abstract: >-
  Operational follow-on to AMEL (Temkit, 2026). Audits LLMBar,
  JudgeBench, and adjacent LLM-judge benchmarks under fresh-context
  vs. AMEL-style batched-context administration; reports
  rank-reshuffle in judge model orderings.
